item.title: Tab ids?
item.dc:creator: @Project_Evolution Project Evolution
item.description:
@Project_Evolution wrote:

0 - Attack Type Tab -1 - Stats Tab -2 - Quests Tab -3 - Inventory Tab -4 - Wearing tab -5 - Prayer Tab -6 - Magic Tab -7 - Empty Tab. This is the tab used for summoning. -8 - Friends List Tab -9 - Ignore List Tab -10 - Logout Tab -11 - Settings Tab -12 - Emotes Tab -13 - Music Tab

These values are negative because they were used in a certain packet I happened to be messing around with.
